modules.description: This module creates and manages animated numeric displays with customizable themes, formats, and update behavior. It works with DOM elements and configuration objects to initialize and control visual odometers on web pages. Use it to render dynamic numeric counters that smoothly transition between values.

This module provides animated numeric displays that can be customized with themes, formats, and update behaviors. It uses DOM elements and configuration objects to create visual odometers that smoothly transition between numeric values. Key operations include initializing displays, updating values, and applying custom styling. For example, it can render a counter that animates from 0 to 1000 with a specified theme and formatting.
